*Dvaput* je trebalo da navratim da bih dostavio pismo. (I had to go twice in order to deliver the letter.)

*Dvaputa* sam slušala priču da bih je potpuno razumela. (I listened to the story twice in order to understand it fully.)

Njegove pohvale su mi *dvaput* toliko značile. (His compliments meant twice as much to me.)

*Dvaputno* smo se bezuspešno trudili da rešimo problem. (We tried to solve the problem twice, but unsuccessfully.)

*Dvaputna* količina sastojaka je pogrešna. (The double amount of ingredients is wrong.)